				To obtain the DF armor you must first start at Cazic. The easiest route would be get a group to camp throne room with you, because now every gorilla drops a decaying armor piece.<BR>
Buy a bar of pp and have a enchanter enchant it for you. Buy all three pieces at once because it seems to be hard to find someone that will enchant it for you.<BR>
Getting in and out of MM to the Undead SK is easier then I thought it would be. Just invis yourself and go to graveyard into crypt. Once in there stand to the right of the coffin and it will drop you right next to the Undead SK. hail him get your pieces then invis yourself again. If you cannot gate out of here, then take hallway up ramp to end. It is a fake entrance so go thru wall there. Then turn left and go thru wall again. Then turn left again and go thru the 3rd fake wall. This puts you behind the crypt. Make sure you stay invis or it gets real ugly.<BR>
Getting to the Undead SK in Najena is very hard and requires a group or high levels with you. He is behind the locked door. And most of the time you will get jumped by a variety of things trying to get armor. So unless you have a group going to protect you while you make exchange with Undead SK chances are you will die tryint to obtain these pieces.<BR>
The other items such as the militia helms and melatite can easily be bought from anyone that is camping the area for exp. most items they will let you loot for free if it is a no drop. But other items are getting more expensive since they are in demand now. And they know we cannot get them ourselves without sudden death.<BR>

				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#D6D1BE">	
		
	
